# ASAccessoryEventType.accessoryAdded

**Case**

The session added an accessory.

## Declaration

```swift
case accessoryAdded
```

## Accessory events

- **ASAccessoryEventType.accessoryChanged**: The properties of an accessory changed.
- **ASAccessoryEventType.accessoryRemoved**: The session removed an accessory.
